  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/672ecf7491cd5dceef65825218e8d9fe.poster.avif?t=1732122547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/672ecf7491cd5dceef65825218e8d9fe.webm?t=1732122547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/672ecf7491cd5dceef65825218e8d9fe.mp4?t=1732122547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UFO Sightings Simulator</strong> is a 3D first-person survival mystery game about shooting photos of paranormal phenomena.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore and discover the <strong>secrets</strong> of the island and the mansion<br></li><li> Shoot <strong>photos</strong> using your camera<br></li><li> Buy items such as rations, decoration, <strong>cows</strong> and a <strong>bike</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Survive</strong> by taking care of your needs like hunger, thirst, and tiredness<br></li><li> Collect all different types of <strong>UFOs</strong> and view them in your <strong>collection</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/5bf3edb2c1dd53dbe4b51b62460d89e6.poster.avif?t=1732122547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/5bf3edb2c1dd53dbe4b51b62460d89e6.webm?t=1732122547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723820/extras/5bf3edb2c1dd53dbe4b51b62460d89e6.mp4?t=1732122547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: